cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.DS, cs.CE 

The paper deals with a transportation problem that involves optimization of cost and pollution factor. This problem can be solved using machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The problem also involves optimization and decision-making (cs.RO) and data structures (cs.DS) for efficient computation. Additionally, the problem has practical applications in civil engineering (cs.CE) for designing transportation systems that minimize pollution.
